&lt;code>transition: [property] [duration] [timing-function] [delay];&lt;/code>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>[CSS] 文字樣式 &amp; 文字斷行</title><link>https://ulagraphy.netlify.com/post/programming-css-font-style/css-font/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2020 22:47:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ulagraphy.netlify.com/post/programming-css-font-style/css-font/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="文字相關的-css-屬性">文字相關的 CSS 屬性
